### ======================================================
### STAGEFLOW - SETTINGS / SALAS (PLANO)
### ======================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@subscriberToken = REPLACE_SUBSCRIBER_TOKEN
@ownerToken = REPLACE_OWNER_TOKEN
@studioId = REPLACE_STUDIO_ID
@otherStudioId = REPLACE_OTHER_STUDIO_ID

### ✅ Criar Sala A
POST {{baseUrl}}/settings/studios/{{studioId}}/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sala A - Ensaio",
  "type": "rehearsal",
  "description": "Ideal para bandas e ensaios com bateria, amplificadores e PA completo.",
  "pricePerHour": 80,
  "capacity": 6,
  "features": ["Bateria acústica", "2 amplificadores", "PA 1000W", "Ar condicionado"],
  "rating": 4.9,
  "reviewCount": 124
}

### ✅ Criar Sala B
POST {{baseUrl}}/settings/studios/{{studioId}}/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sala B - Gravação",
  "type": "recording",
  "description": "Estúdio profissional com tratamento acústico e mesa de som digital.",
  "pricePerHour": 150,
  "capacity": 4,
  "features": ["Mesa digital 32ch", "Microfones Neumann", "Isolamento acústico", "Pro Tools"],
  "rating": 5.0,
  "reviewCount": 89
}

### ✅ Criar Sala C
POST {{baseUrl}}/settings/studios/{{studioId}}/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sala C - Podcast",
  "type": "podcast",
  "description": "Ambiente intimista para gravação de podcasts e conteúdo de áudio.",
  "pricePerHour": 60,
  "capacity": 3,
  "features": ["3 microfones", "Interface Focusrite", "Webcam 4K", "Iluminação LED"],
  "rating": 4.8,
  "reviewCount": 56
}

### ❌ Exceder limite do plano (Starter=1, Professional=3, Enterprise=ilimitado)
### Para Professional, essa 4a criação deve retornar 409 RoomLimitReachedError.
POST {{baseUrl}}/settings/studios/{{studioId}}/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sala D - Extra",
  "type": "extra",
  "description": "Sala adicional para validar limite de plano.",
  "pricePerHour": 90,
  "capacity": 5,
  "features": ["Iluminação", "Ar-condicionado"]
}

### ❌ Token inválido (401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/settings/studios/{{studioId}}/rooms
Authorization: Bearer token-invalido
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sala Token Invalido",
  "type": "test",
  "description": "Teste de auth.",
  "pricePerHour": 50,
  "capacity": 2,
  "features": ["Teste"]
}

### ❌ USER assinante de outro studio não pode operar (403)
POST {{baseUrl}}/settings/studios/{{otherStudioId}}/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sala sem permissão",
  "type": "test",
  "description": "Teste de acesso cruzado por tenant.",
  "pricePerHour": 50,
  "capacity": 2,
  "features": ["Teste"]
}

### ✅ OWNER pode operar em qualquer studio (201/409 conforme limite do plano)
POST {{baseUrl}}/settings/studios/{{studioId}}/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sala criada por owner",
  "type": "owner-test",
  "description": "Teste de permissão global do owner.",
  "pricePerHour": 99,
  "capacity": 4,
  "features": ["Teste"]
}
